---
title: Mexican Style Spiced Beef Chilli in a Bun with Cheese and Slaw
description: Super speedy, this Mexican Style Spiced Chilli in a Bun takes only 15 minutes to make. Traditionally hailing from Mexico, this spicy beef stew is piled into buns and topped with cheese for a quick but flavoursome meal.
